text: Pratima Sherpa (; born 27 November 1999) is the first ranked amateur female golfer from Nepal. She was born and raised in a maintenance shed near the golf course of Royal Nepal Golf Club. Her father, Pasang Sherpa works as a security guard and mother Kalpana Sherpa works as a maintenance worker in Royal Nepal Golf Club. ==References== Nepal Category:Sportspeople from Kathmandu Category:1999 births Category:Living people
